title: Disney CEO says Han Solo’s name is not Han Solo (15 Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
Earlier today Disney CEO Bob Iger revealed a couple of details from the upcoming Young Han Solo film. 
The film will cover the characters life from ages 18 to 24, and will show him obtaining the Millennium Falcon, meeting Chewbacca, and most shocking of all it will show how he took on the name Han Solo. 
Burying the lead a bit, Iger inadvertently revealed that Han Solo is not the space outlaw’s real name! 2
